typeDescriptions.typeString: function (struct IProfile.CandidateProfile storage pointer,struct IProfile.CandidateProfile memory)
function (struct IProfile.CandidateProfile storage pointer,struct IProfile.CandidateProfile memory)
function (address) view returns (struct IProfile.CandidateProfile storage pointer)

addNewProfile((address,address,address,a.details: Requirements: - The profile must not be existent before. - Only contract admin can call this method.

changePubkey(address,bytes).details: Requirements: - The profile must be existed. - Only user with candidate admin role can call this method. - New public key must not be duplicated.

getContract(uint8).details: Returns the address of a contract with a specific role. Throws an error if no contract is set for the specified role.

params.contractType: The role of the contract to retrieve.

returns.contract_: The address of the contract with the specified role.

getId2Profile(address).details: Getter to query full `profile` from `id` address.

registerProfile((address,address,address.details: Requirements: - The profile must not be existent before. - Only user with candidate admin role can call this method.

setContract(uint8,address).details: Sets the address of a contract with a specific role. Emits the event {ContractUpdated}.

params.addr: The address of the contract to set.
params.contractType: The role of the contract to set.

ContractUpdated(uint8,address).details: Emitted when a contract is updated.

Initialized(uint8).details: Triggered when the contract has been initialized or reinitialized.

ProfileAdded(address).details: Event emitted when a profile with `id` is added.

ProfileAddressChanged(address,uint8).details: Event emitted when a address in a profile is changed.

PubkeyChanged(address,bytes).details: Event emitted when the pubkey of the `id` is changed.

ErrDuplicatedInfo(uint8,uint256).details: Error when there is a duplicated info of `value`, which is uin256-padding value of any address or hash of public key, and with value type of `infoType`.

ErrIdAndConsensusDiffer().details: Error when create a new profile whose id and consensus are not identical.

ErrUnauthorized(bytes4,uint8).details: Error indicating that the caller is unauthorized to perform a specific function.

params.expectedRole: The role required to perform the function.
params.msgSig: The function signature (bytes4) that the caller is unauthorized to perform.
